headline: GTA Online
subtitle: GET PLANNING
content: Are you ready to carry out the ultimate heist? Because there’s a whole Diamond just waiting to be mined. If you think you have the brains or brawn to get the job done, then it’s time to take to the planning board and determine your style. Stealth, deception or pure fire power, it’s your heist. Do it your way. Go prep. Go plan. Go prosper.
